{"tid":2321320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保釣二號船主羅堪就被指欠政府逾170萬訟費 遭律政司申請破產","createTime":"2020-12-11T12:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T12:08:54.000Z","uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b70486d119b0683b4dcae33c37573fd006ae3a01","tid":2321320,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:05:05.000Z","msg":"曾成功載著保釣人士登陸釣魚台的「保釣二號」（現稱「啟豐二號」），過去十年牽涉官非不斷，船主羅堪就曾針對海事處阻撓船隻出海一事提出司法覆核，其後又遭裁定非法出海與危及他人海上安全等罪名成立，先後欠下政府共逾170萬元訟費連利息。律政司昨向高等法院呈請羅堪就破產，案件將於明年3月10日聆訊。羅揚言：「錢就唔會還㗎喇，咪申請我破產。」<br />\n<br />\n破產呈請由政府律師孔樂貽代表律政司司長提出。記者致電羅堪就查詢，他指多年來官非不斷，連他本人也弄不清欠款涉及哪一單訴訟，只知道訟費連利息逾177萬元。羅坦言無力償還，即使有錢，「都用嚟維修架船再出海啦」。<br />\n<br />\n羅笑言以現今社會標準，「我哋出海去釣魚台簡直就係愛國行為啦」，<span class=\"red\">批評政府勾結日本勢力打壓愛國保釣人士</span>，故即使有錢也「唔會益呢個喪權辱國嘅政府」，揚言：「錢就唔會還㗎喇，咪申請我破產。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/QYRZCI7LBJASBCEYXLF6S2LHIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FQYRZCI7LBJASBCEYXLF6S2LHIA%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=62894b30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FQYRZCI7LBJASBCEYXLF6S2LHIA%2F&h=5e0cc164\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/QYRZCI7LBJASBCEYXLF6S2LHIA/</a>"},{"pid":"0e951c7194c9bfb7e96b918db2ade38a9f92b23d","tid":2321320,"uid":198216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">大傻閪</span></strong>"},{"pid":"eeaf6b603804f23247f430a6cbf78c9078d03488","tid":2321320,"uid":247048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/vZGzAz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FvZGzAz.gif&h=b2aae6f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc3b2e852592340926af09f0c18f542de14a4091","tid":2321320,"uid":80724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:08:54.000Z","msg":"呢班廢老重未收皮啊？"}]}